 dust emitted during a single\noutburst event with a duration on the order of hours from a single source\nregion corresponding to $\\sim$1\\% of the surface area. A spin period with lower\nlimit on the order of days is suggested to reproduce the coma morphology seen\nin the observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Oct 2019 18:38:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
