asing activity levels,\nultimately becoming filled in; however, we do not find a correlation between\nthe pEW(He IR) and X-ray properties. This behaviour may be attributed to the\nabsence of very inactive stars ($L_{\\rm X}/L_{\\rm bol}$ < -5.5) in our sample\nor to the complex behaviour with regard to increasing depth and filling in.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Nov 2019 08:18:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-27"}
