ery processes. In the extraction process,\nthe same ROI map of the embedding process is recognized without requiring any\nadditional information. Hence, the watermark is blindly extracted from the\nNROI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Nov 2019 13:56:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 May 2020 21:17:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-13"}
