w we can utilize the optimization methods that are popular in optimal\ncontrol literature to help the training of machine learning problems. Finally,\ntwo applications of using a continuous model will be shown in Section 5 and 6\nto demonstrate some of its advantages over traditional neural networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Nov 2019 04:26:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-05"}
